room_title: Escape room "Mad Lab" by Extreme Escape Redding in Redding
room_description: The FBI has hired you to help track down the mad scientist who created and spread a deadly virus throughout your town. It up to you to find the cure hidden in his lab and escape before he returns, finds you, and infects you. You have 60 minutes to crack the codes, find the keys, and the antidote. If you escape with the antidote, you have a chance to save your town. If time runs out you and your town will not survive this madman.
